, 713.7, 805.8]}, {"text": "0.10%, 0.05% and 0% solutions of transgenic cotton genomic DNA were prepared with 100 ng/", "bbox": [252.5, 808.3, 725.6, 822.2]}, {"text": "μL genomic DNA from wild-type K312 and 100 ng/μL genomic DNA from transgenic cotton", "bbox": [252.5, 824.7, 717.5, 838.8]}, {"text": "BG2-7. All of the genomic DNA solutions were used as templates. The sensitivity of selected", "bbox": [252.5, 841.0, 711.0, 855.0]}, {"text": "primers was assessed using PCR. The detection method [13] for PCR amplification products", "bbox": [252.5, 857.5, 712.8, 871.4]}, {"text": "was the same as above.", "bbox": [252.5, 873.9, 365.9, 887.8]}, {"text": "PLOS ONE | DOI:10.1371/journal.pone.0158384 July 5, 2016 4 / 10", "bbox": [45.5, 945.2, 727.3, 956.7]}]}